<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>ajaxLink() helper generates HTML with attribute 'onClick',
which should be lowercase 'onclick'.
(HTML does not validate against XHTML1_STRICT)</p>

<p>To correct this,
change line #257 in ZendX/JQuery/View/Helper/AjaxLink.php:
from:
 $attribs['onClick'] = $js;
to:
 $attribs['onclick'] = $js;</p>

